<br>
As I was ML today, I had the chance to see our current system in action and I have the feeling that it needs some tweaking. I would like to hear your opinion on that.  We never expected the system to be perfect from the start and I got the feeling that some changes should be made. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
I think we should open the system a bit more so more loot is distributed among the participants of the raids. I had the feeling that a lot of people were holding back because they did not want to loose all points on &quot;minor&quot; items or wanted to keep them to have a chance once the &quot;big&quot; stuff rolls in. As you can see in the loot list, only 3 people walked away with something. This is far too little, in my opinion.<br>
<br>
While it is ok that some of the cash goes to the bank for future undertakings, it does not mean that NEARLY ALL of it should be kept by the ML (I was accused of greed at some point but I was only trying to apply the system we set up and add more pp to the SCARAB bank, but it confirmed my impression that the system needs tweaking).<br>
<br>
The best example are the armor drops in Hate. Many of us already have better and would normally skip the rolls. I received many tells on the lines of &quot;I would take it but not if it means losing my points&quot;. The purpose being, of course, turning the items in in PoK for a bit of XP and a gem.<br>
<br>
I think we must have some way of being able to spend a portion of our points on minor items for that purpose. Someone proposed an auction system in one thread. Or if armor drops are not wanted by anybody, they could still be rolled among those who want them. These are just 2 ideas for possible compromises.<br>
<br>
It honestly pains me a bit when I try to do my &quot;job&quot; on a raid and apply a system &quot;under evaluation&quot; and am called things for it I simply cannot &quot;identify with&quot; <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   - as if I was raking in the loot for myself. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
So this is why I want to put this up for further discussion. What would you favor? Or is the current system ok? Would you want to see more loot distributed among the participants? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
Take care,<br>
<br>
Karo/Eti<br>
